metadata.description:
It's cuteness is overloaded with these Baby Apes!The Baby Ape NFT Collection consists of 10,000 distinct NFTs created by TNC ART and will be airdropped only to the Lady Ape Club (LAC) holders! These swag Baby Apes with a hint of gold will be incubating on your STRMNFT account until their DNA is activated.

LAC owners can access 10,000 DNA NFT via STRMNFT (yet to be released) in order to trade their Baby Apes. The incubation period for Baby Apes will vary according to the DNA you purchase.

Instant DNA (100,000 STRM): Buying Instant DNA enables the breeding of Baby Apes; unlocking will happen within 48 hours.

Classic DNA (30,000 STRM): Buying Classic DNA enables the breeding of Baby Apes; unlocking will happen after three months of receiving the Baby Ape airdrop.

Slow DNA (10,000 STRM): Buying Slow DNA enables the breeding of Baby Apes; unlocking will happen after six months of receiving the Baby Ape airdrop.

Your Baby Ape NFT will spend a year in incubation if DNA is not purchased
